title: Start
body:
Stranger: Hey kids! I have a lot of free sweets at home. Do you want to follow me?

		Jake: I love sweets! You are so nice! 

		Jake: Jenny, we will have a lot of sweets today, let's just follow him.

		Jenny: But I feel something is not right and we are not supposed to follow strangers.

		Stranger: Not just sweets, I also have many cute pets at my home, do you want to see them?

		Jenny: Sounds interesting, but can we really go with him?

		[[No thanks.I should not accept anything from stranger.|NoKidnapper]]

		[[Yes,thank you. If you have more, please give me!|Kidnapper]]

title: NoKidnapper
body:
Jenny: Ah! Help! There is a stranger that trying to kidnap us!

		Stranger: This is not good! I better run now!

title: Kidnapper
body: Oh no! The sweet got poison! The stranger is a kidnapper!
